<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If I make this call on a view:</p>

<p>$this-&gt;view-&gt;addHelperPath(HELPER_DIR,"");</p>

<p>I can get helpers in located in directory HELPER_DIR.  In 1.6.0RC1, I get an error saying that the class "_HelperName" is not found in "HelperName.php".  In 1.6.0RC2, the helper files seem to be simply ignored.</p>

